import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Paper, Grid } from '@mui/material';
import StorefrontIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Storefront';
import PeopleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/People';
import Inventory2Icon from '@mui/icons-material/Inventory2';

const Dashboard = ({ clientesCount, productosCount }) => (
  <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
    <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={700} mb={3}>
      <StorefrontIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#3949ab', mr: 1 }} />
      Panel de Control
    </Typography>
    <Grid container spacing={3}>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
        <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
          <PeopleIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#3949ab' }} />
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h6">Clientes</Typography>
            <Typography variant="h4">{clientesCount}</Typography>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
        <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
          <Inventory2Icon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#3949ab' }} />
          <Box>
            <Typography variant="h6">Productos</Typography>
            <Typography variant="h4">{productosCount}</Typography>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  </Box>
);

export default Dashboard;
